author: Ron Kroichick
title: McIlroy struggling to overcome putting woes at Frys.com Open
text: Soon after his round ended Friday, about 5:30 p.m., Rory McIlroy retreated to the practice green at Silverado Resort. He found an empty spot on the far side, away from three other players and a row of spectators lined along the white picket fence.
